message.content: cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.IR. The paper deals with visual question answering, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The approach presented in the paper involves the use of logical patterns and composition of procedures, which are techniques commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of an external knowledge base, which is a technique used in information retrieval (cs.IR).
